The Hydra system comprises all the files in the Hydra distribution.
There is absolutely no guarantee or warranty for this software.  Hydra
is intended to be free software, and eventually it will have a
standard free-software copyright such as the Gnu CopyLeft, but that
isn't set up yet.  See the readme file for further information, and
contact me directly if you have any questions.

